h3 {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #00C4FF;
  margin-top: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
```

### 4.2 数据卡片组件

```css
/* 核心数据卡片 */
.data-card {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2D3A4F 0%, #1A2332 100%);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 24px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.3);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* 数据卡片 - 光效装饰 */
.data-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 4px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0066FF 0%, #00C4FF 100%);
}

/* 数值样式 */
.data-value {
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #FFFFFF;
  font-family: 'DIN Alternate', 'Roboto Mono', monospace;
}

/* 数值单位样式 */
.data-unit {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: #8892A0;
  margin-left: 4px;
}

/* 数据标签 */
.data-label {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #8892A0;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

/* 趋势标识 (增长) */
.trend-up {
  color: #00C48C;
  font-size: 14px;
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
}
```

